Installation Its recommended to install this tool globally with either pipx
$ # If you haven't installed pipx $ curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cs01/pipx/master/get-pipx.py | python3 $ # Then install, using one of the below commands $ pipx install -i https://artifactory.schireson.com/artifactory/api/pypi/pypi/simple lucha  Additionally you can set up shell completion for zsh or bash by evaluating one of the following lines in your .zshrc or .bashrc
# zsh eval &quot;$(_LUCHA_COMPLETE=source_zsh lucha)&quot; # bash eval &quot;$(_LUCHA_COMPLETE=source lucha)&quot;  Example Usage ```bash $ lucha &ndash;help Usage: lucha [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]&hellip;
